Preparing some charts¶

In [18]:
total = df_inf[df_inf['Type'] == 'Country'].shape[0]
nr_charts = math.ceil(total / nr_per_chart)
nr_rows = math.ceil(nr_charts / 2)

fig, axes = plt.subplots(nr_rows, 2, figsize = (20, nr_rows*10), sharex=False)
axes = axes.ravel()

df_temp = df_inf[df_inf['Type'] == 'Country']

for i in range(nr_charts):
    df_unpivot = df_temp.sort_values(by='GDP_2020', ascending=False).iloc[i*nr_per_chart:(i+1)*nr_per_chart].melt(id_vars = ['Country Name', 'Country Code', 'Type', 'GDP_2020'], var_name = 'Year')
    df_unpivot['Year'] = df_unpivot['Year'].astype(int)
    sns.lineplot(data=df_unpivot, x='Year', y='value', hue='Country Name', ax=axes[i])
#     axes[i].set_xticks([c for c in year_cols if (int(c) % 4 == 0)])
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
